# Lookup-service credentials (Phase K.3b + K.3c online providers).
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values. `.env` is gitignored.
# Every key is OPTIONAL — without them the K.3a offline lookup chain
# still returns 6-9 fields per US metro. Online providers add coords +
# solar resource + per-face roof geometry.
#
# Already-set shell env vars win over this file, so rotating a key during
# a session is as easy as `export PVESS_MAPBOX_TOKEN=new` — no .env edit.

# Mapbox public token (recommended: pk.* with URL whitelist).
# Adds: latitude / longitude / county / canonical_address.
# Get one: https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
PVESS_MAPBOX_TOKEN=

# NREL Developer API key. Free signup.
# Adds: solar_irradiance_kwh_m2_day / annual_energy_kwh_per_kw.
# Get one: https://developer.nrel.gov/signup/
PVESS_NREL_API_KEY=

# K.3c — Google Cloud Solar API key. Enable the Solar API in your GCP
# console first, then create an API key restricted to Solar API only.
# Adds: roof_sections[] with per-face pitch / azimuth / area + imagery
# date + Google's estimated max panel count.
# Replaces a $20-40 EagleView report at ~$0.05 / call (buildingInsights).
# Enable: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/solar.googleapis.com
# Pricing: https://developers.google.com/maps/billing-and-pricing/pricing#solar
#
# **TWO SKUS share this key**:
#   * buildingInsights ~$0.05/call — drives `pvess lookup` + the free
#     `pvess roof-vis` analytical view. Cheap, run on every prospect.
#   * dataLayers       ~$0.50/call — drives `pvess roof-vis --satellite`
#     real-imagery render. Reserve for SIGNED CUSTOMERS (deposit paid).
#
# The CLI's `--satellite` flag is gated behind --confirm-cost (one-shot)
# or PVESS_ALLOW_PAID_RENDERS=1 (session-level) so you can't blow
# through your monthly budget on tire-kicker leads.
PVESS_GOOGLE_SOLAR_KEY=

# Optional: lift the per-render cost-confirmation prompt for sales
# reps who've already acknowledged the dataLayers pricing. Setting
# this to "1" / "true" / "yes" lets `pvess roof-vis --satellite` run
# without --confirm-cost. Use sparingly — it's the loaded gun.
# PVESS_ALLOW_PAID_RENDERS=
